      "description": "We are pleased to present this superlative example of automotive engineering, currently held in a state of pristine preservation. This vehicle exhibits an immaculate exterior finish and an interior cabin that remains entirely free of wear, reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. Every mechanical system has undergone a comprehensive diagnostic review to confirm performance that mirrors its original factory specifications. This is a rare opportunity to secure a specimen of unrivaled integrity, suited for the most exacting of collectors.",
