    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one! It\u2019s in absolutely flawless condition, inside and out, and drives like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere! I\u2019m so excited for someone to take this home and enjoy it as much as I have. It's practically brand new and ready for its next adventure. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
