    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E92 BMW M3, a final-run masterpiece of naturally aspirated performance. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio for surgical throttle response. The engine is mated to a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power delivery. Preventative maintenance is complete, including documented rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis remains taut, featuring Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and the signature carbon fiber roof with zero UV degradation. Brakes consist of cross-drilled compound rotors with excellent pad life remaining. This is a mechanically pristine example with a comprehensive service dossier, suited for the most discerning enthusiast.",
